title: Ep 352 - Gokuldham Is Excited About IPL
shortDesc: The entire colony is gathered at Taarak's house and discussing the upcoming IPL match. Just then, Jethalal arrives with a bad news. How will all the members react? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 353 - Ayushman Khurana Visits Gokuldham
shortDesc: Ayushman Khurana visits Gokuldham society and tells them how he's a big fan of Gokuldham Society. He decides to interview the society members. Will the interview go well? Watch to find out.

title: Ep 354 - Champaklal Catches Jethalal With A Bag
shortDesc: The Society men decide to watch a match together with a few drinks. But, they see Champaklal watching the match in Taarak's house. Champaklal sees the bag with alcohol and questions Jetha. Will Jethalal escape from the situation? Watch to find out.

title: Ep 355 - Dayas saree Collection
shortDesc: Jethalal opens Daya's cupboard to look for an important envelope containing quotations from some important client. Later, he finds out that she has a collection of a number of sarees. What's his reaction? Watch this episode to find out.

title: Ep 356 - Women Plan To Go Shopping
shortDesc: While buying vegetables, Daya informs the women about this saree sale that has popped up in the city. All the women plan to go shopping together and buy sarees. Will their husbands let them do so?

title: Ep 357 - Jethalal Understands Daya
shortDesc: Daya wears an old saree and goes to deliver lunch for Jethalal so that he asks her to buy a few new clothes. Before she says anything, Jethalal understands what Daya really wants.

title: Ep 358 - The Ladies Are Scammed
shortDesc: Daya is shocked after she finds more than half of the saris she bought from the sale defective. One after another, all the ladies realize that there is some defect in all the clothes they have bought. What will they do now?

title: Ep 359 - Daya Is In A Fix
shortDesc: When Jethalal asks Daya to show him the saris she has bought, she is anxious. She somehow manages to give an excuse and Jethalal leaves for his shop as he is getting late.

title: Ep 360 - The Ladies Lodge A Police Complaint
shortDesc: After the ladies get checked out of the sari shop, they decide to lodge a police complaint against the shopkeeper. When they go to the police station, a policeman suggests they go to consumer forum to file a complaint.

title: Ep 361 - Garba Andolan
shortDesc: After everyone fails to help, the ladies decide to play Garba in front of the sari shop until the shopkeeper accepts that he has cheated them. Meanwhile, Rita reaches the location and starts covering the 'Garba Andolan.'

title: Ep 362 - Fight For Justice
shortDesc: The fight for justice continues for three hours and the news is broadcasted. After seeing the women in trouble, a minister calls up the police and asks them to take care of the situation.

title: Ep 363 - Ladies Under Arrest
shortDesc: Just when the police arrest the ladies for revolting in a public area, the shopkeepers family arrives. Seeing her daughter lose trust in him, he accepts his mistake and is declared guilty.

title: Ep 364 - Its Christmas For Taarak
shortDesc: Taarak is on cloud nine when Anjali tells him that he can eat whatever he wants for the next eight days. He excitedly asks Anjali to prepare all his favorite dishes for the next eight days.

title: Ep 365 - Abdul Has Competition
shortDesc: One day, Abdul finds a vegetable vendor selling the items he sells. Afraid of incurring a loss, he starts fighting with the vendor. Bhide and Popatlal intervene to stop them. How will they solve the problem?

title: Ep 366 - The War Of Cricket
shortDesc: Bhide complains about the kids playing cricket in the society compound. Jethalal supports the kids and the conversation reaches out of hand. How will everyone react to this? How far will the argument go?
